Products

































Low voltage AC
Boost the productivity of your processes, improve energy efficiency and cut maintenance costs.












Medium voltage AC
Leading international supplier of medium voltage AC drives in the range of 250 kW to more than 100 MW.












DC
The flexibility to design your machine or industrial process to take advantage of this technology.












Drive Services
Improve drive performance, maximize uptime and get rapid assistance and support when you need it.












Connectivity
Multiple options for extending the basic functionality and data transfer capabilities of low voltage AC drives. 












Software tools
These tools provide a user-friendly and easy-to-use approach for the selection, commissioning and use of ABB drives. 














General purpose 
All the essential features built-in, simplifying drive selection, installation and use.




Micro 
Precise speed control and simple integration. 




Machinery 
Premium motor control with hardware flexibility, programmability and scalability for an optimal solution.




Industrial 
Our benchmark of performance, expertise and quality, serving you locally on a global scale.





Industry specific 
Dedicated solutions for industries and applications such as HVAC, elevators, electric heavy working machines, and water & wastewater.




Legacy drives 
Lifecycle management model aimed to provide proactive service offerings for maximizing availability and performance.




Motion control 
Suitable for many different applications, from single to multi-axis machine control.


 






